{"hda4445bfg444bg4fb0g89begfa8487bdae46": ["With fragulous crown, and with sceptre abrade,<br>Dror Ragzlin short work of the innkeeper made!", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "9a2a74f2-cd36-7602-171e-c083e532a81e"], "hca21c418gd38bg4f41g819dg8465d577d95c": ["Hur!", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "28d481c5-2ad9-7d4d-4159-693570a38db0"], "haade88aag0e78g4245gbc84gdb23e458fb04": ["The inn burnt to ash! The captives were many!<br>Goblinkind had reduced them to cowering filfenny!", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "99a757f2-6114-bcb4-78e7-249a242d3d6b"], "h45a4d8eegbfdfg452eg8935g19da324579d4": ["So raiseth your goblets, and drain them with pride!<br>Dror Ragzlin, the True Soul, hath led you galide!", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "e563f223-e40f-b570-3899-62c4099c48e0"], "hb8d01a16g0caag4bedg9243g1212114a4b61": ["Hur! HUR!", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "6be1535e-eeef-19ab-5a9e-30abab17a22e"], "h2dfa3e4egc4fdg4271g815agd0a18a06e6be": ["<i>Give him your rapt attention.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "7e99aad6-880e-0f69-14e3-c3ad6c7be08c"], "haf431400g8356g40dcgb3c1g2e0542b29889": ["'Fragulous'? 'Galide'? I don't know this language.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "ca3e3f28-c60a-4d94-9c9c-b322640fd917"], "h5bde3765gb103g48b1gb216gd3f58c5beef1": ["<i>Common</i>, ye turnip.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "931b44a4-dedc-4ea1-e945-583256f581e0"], "hde1caa41g10a4g435bg8f79gb19b85605cfd": ["Quite so. Now if you'll excuse me.", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "2b2eb28f-fbc3-d8e9-9c1d-e108b3d40a0e"], "h8274e05fg7fc2g471bga04bgbd994da8a43d": ["Bravo!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "8fe2b3fc-28f2-7f2e-a3ad-312f9cce2468"], "hfb3a0b0cga086g4789ga8b9g0699a6c73ee3": ["Whozzat? Friend o' yours? You up to somethin'?", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "644fe713-6745-9ac0-80a7-70c21945ca09"], "hd1cfd2afgcae8g4c1bg9417g06c8d1c4670e": ["Boo! Get off the stage!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "c86c37c9-25c4-a599-eee9-fe544fbfc6b4"], "hd5305829g2853g47c0g9da4g18aa40280437": ["Why, I never-!", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "224eb799-042f-278f-86e2-94db9340a5a8"], "heae1798bg5c2ag4ac0ga7e2ga7c34cfcb3d2": ["You! Move off!", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "99e84b31-b17e-38b5-1a68-f963d6650016"], "h0612a997g0e8dg42f3g9e61gaf5c7832d045": ["<i>(Do as she says. Now!)</i>", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "e380f8b0-7945-a6db-beb5-32f34d2e1860"], "hf0c02a2dg7aaag43e9gbefegcaf48ea36579": ["Ahem: Now where was I?", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "e3d9bf1f-c21e-0f72-1d6c-39c2db33c2d6"], "h6a700f8cg28c8g4d31gaafcg6d5225726ec6": ["Wait a tich. That a friend o' yours?", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "96d1f873-a069-2f18-798e-0e566416c682"], "hed7b46eeg5374g4412g976cgfc052c0bdea9": ["Certainly not!", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "6950b3fd-676f-d033-5e98-2077d46ad615"], "h1e9dc568ge804g4c4fgbfd7gfcd0ac5ff7a0": ["<i>(What are you doing? I'm busy here!)</i>", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "0e49c147-a5c8-708a-3ea7-f72dab270969"], "h6da61112g7b40g4929ga62bgec1a99d1de61": ["You lyin'?", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "98d474a6-9032-c893-cb89-5df4f4b6acdd"], "heb684ec8g9ca1g4ee9ga8ffg68a925267ba3": ["To you? Never!", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "569a6824-20d0-8f22-a7f1-7b655643b26b"], "h4586a9b7g3084g4e27g9ebegf852faab9077": ["Come - let's continue our ballad!", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "1867a528-ba5e-ebe5-f12f-2c8c1d38b4d2"], "h463d6390g2b1ag4efcg84d2ge19c80752ded": ["Ahem. 'Dror Ragzlin, Dror Ragzlin, we, erm...'", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "1fc17eba-3890-75ee-f7b8-ec7bf7862f85"], "hcbe8e4fagede7g4ccegb5a8g1120e7a2f060": ["I reckon Dror Ragzlin's the gobbo in charge, the way this one's carrying on.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "aaabf9fc-37b8-a952-c69b-88c6869005b2"], "h06241eb1g763dg4993gab08gd76ce4723d33": ["I, erm... 'Dror Ragzlin, umtumptous, Dror Ragzlin, erm...'", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "7bedd41f-195d-969a-fe8e-e6de4ea2bbf6"], "hfd5982d0g0271g493cg9972g0045ee2d829f": ["Bahh. You broke 'im!", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "1d9e0301-ad32-095d-8a96-441c23dd4c0d"], "hb99918ecg6c21g47a8ga389g49ba5a47b797": ["Wait! Wait! 'Dror Ragzlin, we... pray... we...'", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "91e9c030-e534-889b-3ceb-b6a42a3877e6"], "h30fd9f37g3e57g487dg8574g95566e51c459": ["C'mon, pigeon. Back to your cage.", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "5e8fc394-976a-5cea-934c-ccc1749ee47c"], "h95265bcbg11aeg4ceeg95b1gadd3ec678752": ["<i>(Now look what you've done!)</i>", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "0416d37d-52a2-f95e-5cd0-3c92ee7e1913"], "h3aae089cge74fg4a0agb9aeg259d44cdcad1": ["No! I mean, I... we've <i>met</i>, but only for the briefest of consultations.", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "229c74f0-7586-66be-9bdd-a53fde18b049"], "h70db70adg2184g4f9aga27eg1582da124270": ["Conspirin', are ye?", "c25f0e79-b9f7-453c-8138-964bca267d93", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "ef46aaf0-8637-5c3d-2124-fdd83ae66e64"], "h64bfc383g053dg4678g84deg1c980921a27c": ["What? No! Please, you misunderstand.", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "454eb7d5-2710-c072-bb40-5a21201bb7be"], "h0f33bbffgddd5g4aa2gba84g70ea7a77d168": ["<i>Grimace at the feeble rhymes.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "0db97adb-31a0-0a50-a5c4-2ead7581317f"], "h14c3bc50gdd08g4332gad4egff417268daf5": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_VoloBallad_Volo_FestivitiesArea.html", "d1d7c77e-2496-59bb-9cc2-5c0533f4ac9c"]}